### Country of birth (Cymraeg)

The typeahead component sends a `lang` parameter in it's query string that matches the `lang` attribtue on the `<html>` element of the page.

The [example API](https://github.com/ONSdigital/typeahead-prototypes-backend-service) sat behind this typeahead will search both the `cy` and the `en-gb` data to find results. If the selects a result from typing the English version of a country name, then the input will be populated with the English name, otherwise it will be populated with the Welsh match.

