## Response object

The typeaheads expect the API response to return a JSON object with two keys:

{% md %}
| Key          | Type                       | Purpose                                                                                                                            |
| ------------ | -------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| results      | Array<TypeaheadResultItem> | The results array                                                                                                                  |
| totalResults | number                     | The total number of results the server found. This may be greater than the number of results returned if results have been limited |
{% endmd %}

### TypeaheadResultItem

The TypeaheadResultItem should consist of at least a key coresponding to the searched language (e.g. `en-gb`) with it's corresponding value.

#### Example response

```
{
    "results": [
        {
            "en-gb": "United Kingdom",
            "cy": "Deyrnas Unedig"
        }
    ],
    "totalResults": 1
}
```

